I'm going to resume our interrogation.

469
00:27:05,230 --> 00:27:08,710
別急  我能看出來  他觸動了你的神經
Not yet. Clearly, he struck a nerve in there.

470
00:27:09,050 --> 00:27:10,650
我沒有殺亞伯拉罕
I didn't kill Abraham.

471
00:27:10,650 --> 00:27:14,180
我相信你  但我要了解他到底在說什么
I believe you, but I need to know what he's talking about.

472
00:27:16,300 --> 00:27:17,580
想告訴我嗎
Want to fill me in?

473
00:27:18,700 --> 00:27:22,160
當卡特里娜打破婚約之后  亞伯拉罕傷心欲絕
Abraham was devastated when Katrina broke her troth to him.

474
00:27:22,880 --> 00:27:23,680
