the two of us were charged with an important clandestine mission,

476
00:27:27,330 --> 00:27:28,110
去護送
to deliver

477
00:27:28,110 --> 00:27:31,790
《第一屆大陸會議決議宣言》
the Declaration of Resolves of the First Continental Congress.

478
00:27:32,150 --> 00:27:33,360
《決議宣言》
Declaration of Resolves?

479
